item.title: 2021-07-29 18:00 Code 'n' Chill Meetup - Norrköping Software Development
item.description: I had the idea that we could code some stuff outside together. So basically bring your laptops and projects. If you don't have a project or laptop and just would like to chat and/or learn a bit from others, that's a great opportunity to do so.
